
Analysis Description
--------------------
 Read an alignment of coding sequences and replace any ambiguous codons
with ---. Write results to a new file in FASTA format, and report
changed sequences to stdout 

- __Requirements__: An MSA

- __Citation__: TBD

- __Written by__: Sergei L Kosakovsky Pond

- __Contact Information__: spond@temple.edu

- __Analysis Version__: 0.1

